Alphabet Tweet
==============

Requirements
-------------

 * Twitter4r >= 0.5.3 (http://twitter4r.rubyforge.org/)
 * Dict (http://www.davep.org/misc/dict.rb)
 
Usage
-----

    $ ./alphabet_tweet.rb
    
Enter username and password when prompted
 
